name: Acer japonicum
description:
Poetree is a series of three and a continuity of the Plant series.
Plants series was created as a therapeutic form of treatment to take my mind off the burnout I am currently living. Using vqgan-clip  with the text prompt from what I see through my window looking at the forest I have the chance to live in.
Then, i manually edit the AI outpout. 
This project is meant to give me the opportunity to get back to my roots as a permaculturist and an artist.
